snippet: Second-seeded Stan Wawrinka has finally won a match at the Dubai Tennis Championships after beating Sergiy Stakhovsky of Ukraine 5-7, 6-3, 7-5 on Tuesday to advance to the second round....
lead_paragraph: Second-seeded Stan Wawrinka has finally won a match at the Dubai Tennis Championships after beating Sergiy Stakhovsky of Ukraine 5-7, 6-3, 7-5 on Tuesday to advance to the second round.

headline.print_headline: Wawrinka Breaks Racket on Way to 1st Win at Dubai Tournament
headline.main: Wawrinka Breaks Racket on Way to 1st Win at Dubai Tournament
